  "text": "The paper [CITATION_1] proposes a formal Petri Net semantics for BPEL which assures exception handling and compensations. Moreover, the authors present the parser which can automatically convert business process diagrams into Petri Net. Consequently, the semantics enabled many Petri Net verification tools to automatically analyze business processes.",
